     2. Server sets stop_requested = True
     3. Next episode's callback POST response returns {"stop": true}
     4. train() saves model, closes logger, returns {"stopped": True}
     5. CLI sets DB status to "stopped"
     6. Latency: at most 1 episode duration (CartPole episodes are typically <1 second)

